{"tid":1449461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察就咁睇根本就唔係燒傷","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:00:58.000Z","uid":136948,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04e7e582fb2677fbacbf33cead83c5b9e6dea2dc","tid":1449461,"uid":136948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"先利申 只係讀過急救 冇讀過醫/護士course<br />\n但係真係睇唔順眼黑警又係到作新聞<br />\n希望各位可以討論下<br />\n<br />\n事源黑警FACEBOOK PAGE 個新POST話有黑警因為「汽油彈引致雙腳<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒傷</span></span></strong>的一名同事」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AYnhdY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AYnhdY.png&h=c948113e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好明顯個傷口邊係有甩皮<br />\n<br />\n但我想比大家睇下本急救書<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXfwU0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXfwU0D.jpg&h=e811effc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒傷既徵狀係冇甩皮架 你仆街就仆街啦<br />\n冇仆死你算好彩呀仲作新聞</span></span>"},{"pid":"7904c41c4407a138f774233d13cbdf5a53f846b4","tid":1449461,"uid":261430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"都係左腳<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/2396758060402459/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftang.earthquake%2Fvideos%2F2396758060402459%2F&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=f6d45afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/2396758060402459/</a>"},{"pid":"310efdda73c1a9b10616cbacebf2d99c5832c1df","tid":1449461,"uid":18894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"火係向上燒既<br />\n點樣可以唔燒中小腿但燒到膝頭<br />\n仲要淨係左右膝頭<br />\n<br />\n成日都跑跑下仆街 <br />\n咪自己認左佢係仆街囉"},{"pid":"67d5340fe99cb35673e34d796d3a7008fcc515ad","tid":1449461,"uid":142989,"like":0,"dislike":